data.description: Step into The Heights of Town Madison and experience the welcoming embrace of this finely crafted traditional-style end unit townhome. The open-concept main level is perfect for entertaining, bathed in an abundance of natural light. The expansive kitchen island offers versatility for casual dining or group gatherings around the table. The first-level master bedroom is generously sized, providing both space and privacy, featuring a separate shower, tub, and a convenient walk-in closet. Upstairs, a spacious loft creates an inviting space for gatherings, complemented by two additional bedrooms connected by a Jack and Jill bathroom. New carpet just installed!  2.5% Assumable VA loan!
